  <div class="case-block">
    <h3>Market Research Case ①</h3>
    <h4>Thailand International School Market (Selfeliz Project)</h4>

    <p>In Bangkok, Thailand, the international school market is expanding, forming community markets composed of affluent households and expatriate professionals.</p>

    <ul>
      <li>Approximately 275 schools nationwide in Thailand</li>
      <li>Approximately 80 schools in Bangkok</li>
      <li>Community population of approximately 300,000</li>
    </ul>

    <p>From this analysis, we identified a new market opportunity — School Community Apparel (apparel for school communities) — and developed a business proposal.</p>
    <p>We prepared both Japanese and English versions and presented them to the partner in Thailand.</p>

