    <h3>Market Research Case ②</h3>
    <h4>Thai Brand HADARA — Japan Market Analysis</h4>

    <p>A comprehensive market analysis for the Japan market entry of HADARA, a Thai bag brand for women.</p>

    <p><strong>Scope of Analysis</strong></p>
    <ul>
      <li>Competitive landscape in the Japanese market</li>
      <li>Purchasing characteristics of Japanese women</li>
      <li>Price segment analysis</li>
      <li>Sales channel analysis</li>
      <li>Analysis of the Thai tourist market in Japan</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Based on the analysis, we developed the following market entry strategies:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Phased rollout starting from Fukuoka</li>
      <li>Japan Premium product development</li>
      <li>Leveraging the Thai tourist market in Japan</li>
      <li>Media exposure strategy</li>
    </ul>

    <p>For this project as well, we prepared both Japanese and English versions and presented them to the Thai brand.</p>

